<!-- index.nunjucks -->
{% extends "layout.nunjucks" %}

{% block title %}
  FreshJones - Direct Mail Marketing
{% endblock %}

{% block header %}
  {{header.active('services')}}
{% endblock %}

{% block main %} 
 
  <section class="hero-stark">
    <div class="wrap wrap-center">
      <div class="section-summary">
        <h1 class="section-topic">Direct Mail Marketing</h1>
        <h2 class="section-heading">Get your message in your customers hands</h2>
        <p class="section-lead">Use direct mail to build personal connections with your customers.</p>
        <p>
          {{ button.link('/contact.html', 'Tell Me More') }}
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="services-intro">
    <div class="wrap wrap-center wrap-center-narrow">
      <div class="section-spaced">
        <div class="section-summary">
          <h1 class="section-heading">Everyone likes getting mail.</h1>
          <p>Even the most phone-addicted among us light up when an interesting package shows up in the mailbox with our name on it.</p>
          <p>And as a business what other method of deliver puts your message directly into the hands of your potential customers?</p>
          <p>Direct mail is an excellent way to connect with your customers in ways that are personal, highly engaging, trust-building and memorable. People feel closer to things they can see and touch.</p>
          <p>Using direct mail as part of your cohesive marketing strategy can help you driving more demand for your products and services, build more leads for your sales team and attract more customers and higher sales, all leading to one specific purpose...to grow your business.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div> 
  </section>

  <section class="services-intro">
    <div class="wrap wrap-center wrap-center-narrow">
      <div class="section-spaced">
        <div class="section-summary">
          <h1 class="section-heading">Direct Mail Marketing Services</h1>
        </div>
        <div>
          <ul class="flex-blocks flex-blocks-center">
            <li>Product/Service Catalogs</li>
            <li>Discounts or Specials</li>
            <li>Postcard Mailers</li>
            <li>Announcements</li>
            <li>Sample Giveaways</li>
            <li>Reminders</li>
            <li>Newsletters</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p>Not sure which solution is right for you? Give us a call we’ll help you determine the best options for your needs.</p>
          {{ button.link('/contact.html', 'Lets get started') }}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div> 
  </section>

