        </div>
        <div>
          <ul class="section-list section-list-bullets">
            <li>Direct Mail Stands Out</li>
            <li>Direct mail is memorable</li>
            <li>People read their mail</li>
            <li>Great ROI</li>
            <li>Build authority and trust</li>
            <li>High levels of engagement and focused attention without multitasking</li>
            <li>More formal that email</li>
            <li>Has influence over purchasing power</li>
            <li>More personal</li>
            <li>Tangible, able to create an impactful sincere physical experience</li>
            <li>Its familiar and people understand it and are receptive of it</li>
            <li>Its highly personal and personalizable</li>
            <li>People like getting mail</li>
            <li>Target people who are less active online (boomers, older)</li>
            <li>You want a competitive advantage</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div> 
  </section>

