            <li>direct mail that make you stand above your competition</li>
            <li>We always start strategically</li>
            <li>We are results-focused</li>
            <li>We know how to inspire response</li>
            <li>We deal with the technical requirements so you don’t need to</li>
            <li>We take care of the logistics, printing, mailhouse</li>
            <li>We’re fast, we can meet your tight timeframes</li>
            <li>Your print ads will be professional quality</li>
            <li>Always drive back online</li>
            <li>Always take a holistic approach to all marketing tactics</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div> 
